    "name": "人魅",
    "steam_appid": 2128940,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128940/extras/95c4d7cf6f31b62fa998d66379002e3d.avif?t=1757584290\" width=600 height=1236 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128940/extras/4e307cc8389bb24f72fd78134c26100c.webp?t=1757584290\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br><br>《人魅》是第一视角多人恐怖解密游戏。多名玩家通过探索合作，解开故事的谜题，了解在灵异事件背后的真相。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128940/extras/5e2441bc14ff0041ff42d2076eeced85.webp?t=1757584290\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br><br>我们真实还原了乡村小镇的真实环境，通过一系列实地考察之后，我们尽全力给大家呈现出一个狭窄的街道，包括墙上海报，乡村小镇上常见的物件。同时，增加了部分场景道具互动，和故事剧情结合起来，让解密不再生硬。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128940/extras/da2814840ecaa66a5bbc454d814837e7.poster.avif?t=1757584290\" width=600 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128940/extras/da2814840ecaa66a5bbc454d814837e7.webm?t=1757584290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128940/extras/da2814840ecaa66a5bbc454d814837e7.mp4?t=1757584290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128940/extras/3b79e7d797315c7cae24f6af18139787.webp?t=1757584290\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>游戏中支持4名玩家合作通关。在解密和探索的过程中，可以体验到设置机关，破解谜题，分角色的剧情演出等环节。感觉就像大家合作参与了一部互动电影。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128940/extras/3067f795a55f63696859d9c34367cb2e.poster.avif?t=1757584290\" width=600 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128940/extras/3067f795a55f63696859d9c34367cb2e.webm?t=1757584290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128940/extras/3067f795a55f63696859d9c34367cb2e.mp4?t=1757584290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128940/extras/8f0a75d669f1213e52aba019fbed2fb2.webp?t=1757584290\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>在整个游戏中，我们添加了丰富的镜头故事表现，增加了生动的角色配音和大量的剧情文本。同时，在主线流程之外，对于不同角色的背景塑造，我们进行了详细补充说明和相关剧情彩蛋，希望大家可要在游玩的同时更深切的感受到每个角色的心路历程。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128940/extras/f5ea59049e67c97497736a9a11e907e1.avif?t=1757584290\" width=600 height=710 /></span>",
